Updates PK parameter tables (patab)

Source: R/update_pk_tables.R
update_pk_tables.Rd

E.g. useful to call after pharmr::add_peripheral_compartment() to update the $TABLE with parameter estimates

Usage

update_pk_tables(model, ...)

Arguments

model

pharmpy model object or NONMEM model code (character) or path to NONMEM model file.

...

passed to add_default_output_tables()
